## A Quick Mindfulness Reset for Insurance Stress

If you feel overwhelmed while gathering your Medicare documents or reviewing plan options, take a moment to regulate your nervous system. **Riaz Counseling** frequently teaches the **5-4-3-2-1 grounding technique** to help clients pull their brains out of future-oriented worry and back into the present moment:

- Identify **5** things you can see around you right now.
- Identify **4** things you can physically feel (e.g., the chair underneath you, your clothing).
- Identify **3** distinct things you can hear in your environment.
- Identify **2** things you can smell.
- Identify **1** thing you can taste.

