## Frequently Asked Questions

### Is HealthSpring Medicare Advantage the same as Cigna, and how does it relate to riaz counseling?

HealthSpring Medicare Advantage is not simply the same as Cigna today, though the brands were linked in the past. Cigna sold its Medicare business. If you are exploring counseling or mental health support, also confirm which Medicare plans cover those services and whether the provider is in network.

### Can I use HealthSpring Medicare Advantage for counseling or therapy sessions?

HealthSpring Medicare plans may cover counseling or other mental health care as part of your health care coverage, but benefits depend on the specific plan and provider network. Before booking therapy, check your plan documents and confirm that the counseling provider participates in your plan’s network.

### Are there HealthSpring Medicare Advantage plans available throughout Texas?

HealthSpring Medicare Advantage plans are available in Texas, but not every plan is offered in every county. Your service area determines what Medicare plans you can choose. Always check local availability and your preferred health care provider, including any mental health professionals, before enrolling.

